* [http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/ancient/egyptians/ BBC History: Egyptians]<U+2014>provides a reliable general overview and further links
* [http://www.ancient.eu.com/egypt/ Ancient History Encyclopedia] on Egypt
* [http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN&id=9ToLAAAAIAAJ&dq=PtahHotep&as_brr=1 Ancient Egyptian Science: A Source Book Door Marshall Clagett, 1989]
